creator: ViroSoft Studio
descriptionHtml:
The Gospel Faith Mission International (GOFAMINT) Gospel Hymn book in English and Yoruba languages.
The app's simple and friendly interface allows you easily locate and sing your favourite hymns on the go, right from your phone anytime.

FEATURES:
- Number and title search
- Numerical and alphabetical indexes
- Hymn category list
- Text zoom in/out
- Add hymns to favourite
- Hymns sharing
- Three color theme options for user reading convenience.
- Wake lock (prevents device from sleeping while user is reading)
- GOFAMINT Sunday school anthem
- Hymns keyboard tune - (PREMIUM FEATURE).
descriptionShort: The Gospel Faith Mission International (GOFAMINT) Gospel Hymn book.
